  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: The Turning Of Heaven
---
The prime minister said, "I have heard that where affection is lacking,
there will be no love, and if there is no love, there will be no filial
piety. Can you possibly say that perfect benevolence is unfilial?"
